milestones.description: Aayan Afzal Khan and Hazrat Bilal's 83-run partnership is UAE's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 70 between Rohan Mustafa and Zahoor Khan
Malla and Aasif Sheikh's 122-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 95 between Malla and Aasif Sheikh
Airee has broken the record for most ducks (6) in ODIs for NEP, going past Lamichhane's 5
